snippet.title: THESE TREES ARE SPECTRAL FINGERS Trailer
snippet.description:
THESE TREES ARE SPECTRAL FINGERS - Your car has broken down in the middle of nowhere. Surrounded by age-old trees, you walk down the road in search of help,... with no idea of what lurks in these old forests.

Debut game from kavvkka 

Available now at: http://patreon.com/puppetcombo
